{"ja317:0.1":"Jataka ","ja317:0.2":"Catukkanipata ","ja317:0.3":"Pucimandavagga ","ja317:0.4":"7. Matarodanajataka ","ja317:1.1":"“Matam matam evam rodatha, ","ja317:1.2":"Na hi tam rodatha yo marissati; ","ja317:1.3":"Sabbepi sariradharino, ","ja317:1.4":"Anupubbena jahanti jivitam. ","ja317:2.1":"Devamanussa catuppada, ","ja317:2.2":"Pakkhigana uraga ca bhogino; ","ja317:2.3":"Samhi sarire anissara, ","ja317:2.4":"Ramamanava jahanti jivitam. ","ja317:3.1":"Evam calitam asanthitam, ","ja317:3.2":"Sukhadukkham manujesvapekkhiya; ","ja317:3.3":"Kanditaruditam niratthakam, ","ja317:3.4":"Kim vo sokaganabhikirare. ","ja317:4.1":"Dhutta ca sonda akata, ","ja317:4.2":"bala sura ayogino; ","ja317:4.3":"Dhiram mannanti baloti, ","ja317:4.4":"ye dhammassa akovida”ti. ","ja317:5.1":"Matarodanajatakam sattamam. "}